text: Further on down the line in the comment sections you'll see people crapping on comments like the above one. Sort of mocking someone who points out little details and then gets a bunch of chubbies for it. That's part of the reason I like these earlier strip's comment sections. The raised eyebrow does add different tone to the last panel and someone who missed it the first time probably appreciates having it pointed out. Uh...guess what I'm trying to say is well done.
